channel.title: Help!
channel.description: I installed mopar, and it's on my desktop, but when I bring it up it says,"Could not find the main mass. Program will exit." What should I do. The website is just a grey screen, if that's any information. :confused:

item.title: Help!
item.dc:creator: @jehanne jehanne
item.description:
@jehanne wrote:

you can use commands, example

item id of white partyhat is 1048
use the command ::pickup 1048 1
and you will have a phat in your invent

so just type ::pickup 1048 1 in your chat
or type ::pickup 1049 2000 in your chat for 2000 noted white phats
